          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0352P0_20000621_WH_51'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-hanson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0352P0_20000621_WH_51' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Hanson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-hanson" title="Mr David Hanson">Mr. Hanson</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
