            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_77wh' title='Col. 77WH &mdash; HC Deb 21 June 2000 vol 352 c77WH' name='column_77wh' href='#column_77wh' rel='bookmark'>77WH</a>
            The Committee's report is an excellent document&#x2014;it is critical, comprehensive and readable. It has strong conclusions. I hope that the Ministers who read it will take the feedback from the Committee and the people of Wales right to the top so that it will influence the Chancellor of the Exchequer when he makes his announcements on the comprehensive spending review in July.
